{"pageProps":{"entries":[{"title":"N’est-pas mégalo d’avoir son propre site ?","date":"2021-12-17T08:00:00.000Z","draft":false,"id":"n-est-pas-megalo-d-avoir-son-propre-site","content":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Cette question m’a été posée récemment et j’avoue qu’elle m’a un peu abasourdi. Je ne m’y attendais pas.","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":1,"column":105,"offset":104}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":1,"column":105,"offset":104}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bien-sûr que chacun⋅e peut disposer de son propre nom comme il/elle l’entend. Et je ne fais pas exception à la règle.","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1,"offset":106},"end":{"line":3,"column":118,"offset":223}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1,"offset":106},"end":{"line":3,"column":118,"offset":223}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"En arrière fond de cette affirmation, se trouve, bien-sûr, la volonté de discréditer ma parole, en me faisant passer pour un nombriliste, c’est le jeu des élections... comme on ne voudrait plus le voir.","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1,"offset":225},"end":{"line":5,"column":203,"offset":427}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1,"offset":225},"end":{"line":5,"column":203,"offset":427}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"J’ai créé ce morceau d’Internet pour des raisons politiques et pour exprimer mon avis sur les sujets qui me tiennent à cœur, pas pour flatter mon ego.","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1,"offset":429},"end":{"line":7,"column":151,"offset":579}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1,"offset":429},"end":{"line":7,"column":151,"offset":579}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"L’occasion pour moi de vous flécher vers le site Internet de quelques personnes dont j’aime les écrits : ","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1,"offset":581},"end":{"line":9,"column":106,"offset":686}}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://www.davidcormand.fr/","children":[{"type":"text","value":"David Cormand","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":107,"offset":687},"end":{"line":9,"column":120,"offset":700}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":106,"offset":686},"end":{"line":9,"column":151,"offset":731}}},{"type":"text","value":", ","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":151,"offset":731},"end":{"line":9,"column":153,"offset":733}}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://twitter.com/marinetondelier","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Marine Tondelier","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":154,"offset":734},"end":{"line":9,"column":170,"offset":750}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":153,"offset":733},"end":{"line":9,"column":208,"offset":788}}},{"type":"text","value":", ","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":208,"offset":788},"end":{"line":9,"column":210,"offset":790}}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://blogs.mediapart.fr/alain-coulombel","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Alain Coulombel","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":211,"offset":791},"end":{"line":9,"column":226,"offset":806}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":210,"offset":790},"end":{"line":9,"column":271,"offset":851}}},{"type":"text","value":" et, bien-sûr, ","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":271,"offset":851},"end":{"line":9,"column":286,"offset":866}}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://www.facebook.com/stephanie.stiernon.1","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Stéphanie Stiernon","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":287,"offset":867},"end":{"line":9,"column":305,"offset":885}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":286,"offset":866},"end":{"line":9,"column":353,"offset":933}}},{"type":"text","value":".","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":353,"offset":933},"end":{"line":9,"column":354,"offset":934}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1,"offset":581},"end":{"line":9,"column":354,"offset":934}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":935}}}},{"title":"Êtes-vous pour interdire la viande ?","date":"2021-11-08T08:00:00.000Z","draft":false,"id":"etes-vous-pour-interdire-la-viande","content":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Un autre grand thème cher à nos détracteurs et détractrices, la viande ! Selon elleux, les écologistes souhaitent priver l’humanité du plaisir d’en manger.","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":1,"column":156,"offset":155}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":1,"column":156,"offset":155}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"En tant qu’omnivore, bien entendu, je n’ai aucun problème avec le fait de manger de la viande.","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1,"offset":157},"end":{"line":3,"column":95,"offset":251}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1,"offset":157},"end":{"line":3,"column":95,"offset":251}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"En revanche, la souffrance infligée aux animaux dans certaines exploitations (ou plutôt devrais-je dire, usines), n’est pas acceptable ! Je suis parfaitement aligné avec le fait que l’agriculture industrielle (et donc l’élevage industriel) sont néfastes, même si cela signifie de la viande un peu plus chère et donc, que l’on en mangerait un peu moins souvent.","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1,"offset":253},"end":{"line":5,"column":361,"offset":613}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1,"offset":253},"end":{"line":5,"column":361,"offset":613}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Et cela tombe bien ! Selon ","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1,"offset":615},"end":{"line":7,"column":28,"offset":642}}},{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://www.carbone4.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Publication-Carbone-4-Faire-sa-part-pouvoir-responsabilite-climat.pdf","children":[{"type":"text","value":"une étude de Carbone 4","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":29,"offset":643},"end":{"line":7,"column":51,"offset":665}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":28,"offset":642},"end":{"line":7,"column":175,"offset":789}}},{"type":"text","value":" (p. 7), environ 18.51% de notre empreinte carbone individuelle serait due à notre alimentation, dont, principalement, la consommation de viande.","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":175,"offset":789},"end":{"line":7,"column":320,"offset":934}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1,"offset":615},"end":{"line":7,"column":320,"offset":934}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"On peut donc, en mangeant moins de viande, réduire significativement notre enpreinte carbone. C’est de plus meilleur pour la santé !","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1,"offset":936},"end":{"line":9,"column":133,"offset":1068}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1,"offset":936},"end":{"line":9,"column":133,"offset":1068}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Enfin, manger moins de viande, c’est aussi permettre une offre de meilleure qualité (donc, une viande meilleure pour la santé) et du stockage carbone dans les près grâce à l’élevage pastoral.","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":1070},"end":{"line":11,"column":192,"offset":1261}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":1070},"end":{"line":11,"column":192,"offset":1261}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bref, sans interdire la viande, on peut remettre en cause son statut d’aliment roi, pour notre santé et contre le réchauffement climatique !","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1,"offset":1263},"end":{"line":13,"column":141,"offset":1403}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1,"offset":1263},"end":{"line":13,"column":141,"offset":1403}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":1404}}}},{"title":"Êtes-vous pour interdire la voiture ?","date":"2021-11-08T08:00:00.000Z","draft":false,"id":"etes-vous-pour-interdire-la-voiture","content":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Le sujet mérite plus qu’une simple réponse dans cette FAQ et je me plierai à l’exercice le moment venu.","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":1,"column":104,"offset":103}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":1,"column":104,"offset":103}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Cependant, je tiens dors et déjà à rassurer mes concitoyen·nes, je ne souhaite pas que les voitures soient interdites. J’en possède une moi-même qui nous sert peu, mais dont l’usage est important pour des raisons familiales.","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1,"offset":105},"end":{"line":3,"column":225,"offset":329}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1,"offset":105},"end":{"line":3,"column":225,"offset":329}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"D’ailleurs, personne, sérieusement, parmi les écologistes ne pense à cela. C’est surtout un chiffon rouge agité par nos adversaires pour tenter de nous décrédibiliser.","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1,"offset":331},"end":{"line":5,"column":168,"offset":498}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1,"offset":331},"end":{"line":5,"column":168,"offset":498}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Il faut cependant que la voiture perde du terrain. En ville, évidemment, mais partout ailleurs quand c’est possible. Pour ce faire de nombreuses voies sont empruntables et, le moins qu’on puisse dire, c’est qu’elles sont à peine explorées, à ce jour, par les pouvoirs publics.","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1,"offset":500},"end":{"line":7,"column":277,"offset":776}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1,"offset":500},"end":{"line":7,"column":277,"offset":776}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Donc, oui à la voiture quand il n’y a pas d’alternative (j’ai moi même vécu à la campagne un bon nombre d’années et je sais combien cet outil y est central).","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1,"offset":778},"end":{"line":9,"column":158,"offset":935}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1,"offset":778},"end":{"line":9,"column":158,"offset":935}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Mais non à la voiture reine de tous les espaces et de tous les investissements (on se souvient des milliards concédés aux industriels automobiles par Emmanuel Macron, mais aussi plus récemment à Renault pour l’implantation de l’usine Envision).","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":937},"end":{"line":11,"column":245,"offset":1181}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":937},"end":{"line":11,"column":245,"offset":1181}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":1182}}}},{"title":"Avez-vous viré Jackie Avenel ?","date":"2021-08-08T08:46:42.567Z","draft":false,"id":"avez-vous-vire-jackie-avenel","content":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Dans un article de \"La Voix du Nord\", Mr Avenel m’a accusé de l’avoir \"viré\" du groupe local Europe-Écologie les Verts de Douai.","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":1,"column":129,"offset":128}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":1,"column":129,"offset":128}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Bien-entendu, je vous rassure, il n’en est rien. EÉLV est un parti où la démocratie et la décision collective ont une importance capitale.","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1,"offset":130},"end":{"line":3,"column":139,"offset":268}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1,"offset":130},"end":{"line":3,"column":139,"offset":268}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Simplement, ce dernier n’a pas digéré le fait que nos militant·es ne se reconnaissent pas en lui, ni en ses choix, lors de sa mandature en tant qu’adjoint au cadre de vie de la ville de Douai et conseiller communautaire à Douaisis Agglo.","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1,"offset":270},"end":{"line":5,"column":238,"offset":507}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1,"offset":270},"end":{"line":5,"column":238,"offset":507}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Parmi les décisions qui lui ont été reprochées, on peut citer :","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1,"offset":509},"end":{"line":7,"column":64,"offset":572}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1,"offset":509},"end":{"line":7,"column":64,"offset":572}}},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"start":null,"spread":false,"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":false,"checked":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"son vote favorable au boulodrome à 9.5M€ initié par Christian Poiret,","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":3,"offset":576},"end":{"line":9,"column":72,"offset":645}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":3,"offset":576},"end":{"line":9,"column":72,"offset":645}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1,"offset":574},"end":{"line":9,"column":72,"offset":645}}},{"type":"listItem","spread":false,"checked":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"la clôture du parc Bertin (et la mise en difficulté des cyclistes traversant le parc dû au tourniquet positionné à l’entrée),","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":3,"offset":648},"end":{"line":10,"column":128,"offset":773}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":3,"offset":648},"end":{"line":10,"column":128,"offset":773}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":646},"end":{"line":10,"column":128,"offset":773}}},{"type":"listItem","spread":false,"checked":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"ses sorties caractérielles et irrespectueuses des personnes osant le contredire.","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":3,"offset":776},"end":{"line":11,"column":83,"offset":856}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":3,"offset":776},"end":{"line":11,"column":83,"offset":856}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":774},"end":{"line":11,"column":83,"offset":856}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1,"offset":574},"end":{"line":11,"column":83,"offset":856}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Je trouve cela triste de devoir me justifier, mais avec l’article de la Voix du Nord qui est resté en ligne malgré le dementi du groupe local, je n’ai guère le choix que d’utiliser ce blog pour rétablir la vérité...","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1,"offset":858},"end":{"line":13,"column":216,"offset":1073}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":1,"offset":858},"end":{"line":13,"column":216,"offset":1073}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"link","title":null,"url":"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hXTDEWiWoi3v45mf9cv2ClkKcVUymAQu/view?usp=sharing","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lire le communiqué d’EÉLV Douaisis à ce sujet","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":2,"offset":1076},"end":{"line":15,"column":47,"offset":1121}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1,"offset":1075},"end":{"line":15,"column":132,"offset":1206}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1,"offset":1075},"end":{"line":15,"column":132,"offset":1206}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":15,"column":132,"offset":1206}}}},{"title":"Une personne dit être bannie de votre page Facebook / Twitter ?","date":"2021-08-08T08:46:42.567Z","draft":false,"id":"une-personne-dit-etre-bannie-de-votre-page-facebook-twitter","content":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"C’est possible, si tel est le cas, voici les différents cas de figure :","position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":1,"column":72,"offset":71}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":1,"column":72,"offset":71}}},{"type":"list","ordered":false,"start":null,"spread":false,"children":[{"type":"listItem","spread":false,"checked":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"des insultes, menaces ou propos tendancieux et/ou incohérents on été formulés, dans ce cas, ils ont été supprimés et la personne bannie,","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":3,"offset":75},"end":{"line":3,"column":139,"offset":211}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":3,"offset":75},"end":{"line":3,"column":139,"offset":211}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1,"offset":73},"end":{"line":3,"column":139,"offset":211}}},{"type":"listItem","spread":false,"checked":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"des actions négatives répétées, de nature à provoquer le désordre dans les différents débats / commentaires ont été relevés,","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":3,"offset":214},"end":{"line":4,"column":127,"offset":338}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":3,"offset":214},"end":{"line":4,"column":127,"offset":338}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":212},"end":{"line":4,"column":127,"offset":338}}},{"type":"listItem","spread":false,"checked":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"du spam pour obtenir de la visibilité à mon détriment a été envoyé,","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":3,"offset":341},"end":{"line":5,"column":70,"offset":408}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":3,"offset":341},"end":{"line":5,"column":70,"offset":408}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1,"offset":339},"end":{"line":5,"column":70,"offset":408}}},{"type":"listItem","spread":false,"checked":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"des propos de nature à engager ma responsabilité ont été tenus.","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":3,"offset":411},"end":{"line":6,"column":66,"offset":474}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":3,"offset":411},"end":{"line":6,"column":66,"offset":474}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":1,"offset":409},"end":{"line":6,"column":66,"offset":474}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1,"offset":73},"end":{"line":6,"column":66,"offset":474}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ce n’est jamais une décision facile de bannir quelqu’un⋅e, mais mon objectif premier est d’informer les personnes en droit de voter des raisons pour lesquelles l’écologie politique répond aux enjeux contemporains et de répondre à leurs interrogations.","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":476},"end":{"line":8,"column":252,"offset":727}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":476},"end":{"line":8,"column":252,"offset":727}}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Chacun⋅e reste, bien sûr, libre de poster et d’engager sa propre responsabilité sur son compte personnel, mes publications restent partageables par toutes et tous. La liberté d’expression est donc respectée, même si l’audience ne sera pas forcément au rendez-vous 😉.","position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":729},"end":{"line":10,"column":268,"offset":996}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":10,"column":1,"offset":729},"end":{"line":10,"column":268,"offset":996}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":1,"column":1,"offset":0},"end":{"line":11,"column":1,"offset":997}}}}]},"__N_SSG":true}